Keep your search history safe and secured!!
Easily search the web for FREE and keep your data safe from other users.
Delete your history with one click!!
Just click on the extension icon and start browsing the web in incognito mode.

By installing this extension, Anonymous-Search will change your Chrome Default Search.

You can search music artists, songs, albums, images, videos and more while keeping your search history hidden.
Anonymous-Search will:
• Help you protect your privacy.
• Keep your searches private.
• Prevent Chrome from keeping cookies and site data.

Please read carefully: By clicking the “ADD TO CHROME” button in the top right hand corner and installing the AnonymousSearch Tab extension, you accept and agree to installing this AnonymousSearch Tab Chrome extension and setting Chrome™ New Tab to that provided by the service, and you agree to the End User License Agreement and the Privacy Policy and to receiving any future updates and upgrades. You can uninstall the extension at any time.

How to remove our extension from Chrome browser:
 
1) Click on the three horizontal lines icon in the upper right-hand corner of your Chrome browser.
2) Go to "Settings".
3) In the menu that appears click on "Extensions".
4) From the list of installed Extensions, find the name of the extension you wish to uninstall.
5) Click on the trash can icon to the right of "Enable" (for the extension you wish to uninstall).
6) Our extension should be removed from your Chrome browser.
